{
  "chapter_id": 2,
  "title": "Тени сомнения",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "ch2_s1",
      "order": 1,
      "background": "bg_ch2_forest_edge",
      "dialogues": [

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d01",
          "order": 1,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "Чем дальше ты уходишь от мельницы, тем сильнее мир вокруг начинает меняться.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d02"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d02",
          "order": 2,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "Сначала исчезает запах лугов.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d03"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d03",
          "order": 3,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "Потом — тепло солнца.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d04"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d04",
          "order": 4,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "Потом — сами звуки жизни.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d05"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d05",
          "order": 5,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "pause_before": 1.0,
          "text": "Дорога под лапами становится сырой и вязкой.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d06"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d06",
          "order": 6,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "Будто земля здесь никогда полностью не высыхала.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d07"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d07",
          "order": 7,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "camera_effect": "pan_up",
          "text": "Огромные ветви смыкаются над головой.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d08"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d08",
          "order": 8,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "Между ними почти не остаётся света.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d09"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d09",
          "order": 9,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "Только редкие бледные лучи, теряющиеся среди тумана.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d10"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d10",
          "order": 10,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "pause_before": 1.5,
          "text": "Каждый шаг сапог звучит слишком громко.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d11"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d11",
          "order": 11,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "Грязь чавкает под ногами.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d12"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d12",
          "order": 12,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "Где-то далеко трещит сухая ветка.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d13"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d13",
          "order": 13,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "И сразу после этого — тишина.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d14"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d14",
          "order": 14,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "pause_before": 2.0,
          "text": "— Мррр…",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d15"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d15",
          "order": 15,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "— Ненавижу такие леса.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d16"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d16",
          "order": 16,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "— Всё вроде обычное.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d17"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d17",
          "order": 17,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "— Корни. Грязь. Камни.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d18"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d18",
          "order": 18,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "— Но воздух здесь неправильный.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d19"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d19",
          "order": 19,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "pause_before": 1.0,
          "text": "— Будто лес прямо сейчас решает…",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d20"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d20",
          "order": 20,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "— Сожрать меня сразу…",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d21"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d21",
          "order": 21,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_canopy",
          "text": "— Или сначала немного поиграть.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d22"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d22",
          "order": 22,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork",
          "transition_before": "fade_in",
          "text": "Спустя некоторое время лес расступается.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d23"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d23",
          "order": 23,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork",
          "text": "Ты выходишь на длинную узкую поляну.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d24"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d24",
          "order": 24,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork",
          "text": "Дорога впереди раскалывается на три пути.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d25"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d25",
          "order": 25,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork_mud",
          "camera_effect": "panorama",
          "text": "Справа тропа резко уходит вниз.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d26"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d26",
          "order": 26,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork_mud",
          "text": "Там чёрная вязкая грязь и шум бурной воды.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d27"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d27",
          "order": 27,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "Прямо начинается тёмный коридор.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d28"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d28",
          "order": 28,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "Ветки смыкаются так плотно, что внутри почти нет света.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d29"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d29",
          "order": 29,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_rocky",
          "text": "Слева поднимается острый каменистый склон.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d30"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d30",
          "order": 30,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_rocky",
          "text": "Тёмные обломки базальта торчат из земли как клыки.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d31"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d31",
          "order": 31,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork",
          "pause_before": 1.0,
          "text": "— Три дороги.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d32"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d32",
          "order": 32,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_fork",
          "text": "— И ни одной хорошей идеи.",
          "has_choices": true,
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d32_c1",
              "text": "К воде.",
              "effects": {
                "adaptability": 0.07,
                "activity": 0.05,
                "selfControl": -0.03
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d40"
            },
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d32_c2",
              "text": "В тёмный лесной тоннель.",
              "effects": {
                "rigidity": 0.07,
                "negativeAffect": 0.05,
                "sociality": -0.07
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d50"
            },
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d32_c3",
              "text": "Вверх по скалам.",
              "effects": {
                "selfControl": 0.07,
                "egoFocus": 0.05,
                "emotionalSensitivity": -0.05
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d60"
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d40",
          "order": 40,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_mud_river",
          "transition_before": "fade_in",
          "text": "Ты шагаешь прямо в грязь.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d41"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d41",
          "order": 41,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_mud_river",
          "text": "Холодная жижа мгновенно облепляет сапоги.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d42"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d42",
          "order": 42,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_mud_river",
          "text": "Земля словно пытается удержать тебя.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d43"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d43",
          "order": 43,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_mud_river",
          "text": "Рядом ревёт река.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d44"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d44",
          "order": 44,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_mud_river",
          "text": "Шум воды постепенно вытесняет мысли.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d45"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d45",
          "order": 45,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_mud_river",
          "pause_before": 1.0,
          "text": "— Попробуй теперь найти меня, лес.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d70"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d50",
          "order": 50,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "transition_before": "darkening",
          "text": "Ты входишь под свод деревьев.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d51"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d51",
          "order": 51,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "Мир вокруг резко меняется.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d52"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d52",
          "order": 52,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "Ветер исчезает.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d53"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d53",
          "order": 53,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "Даже собственные шаги звучат приглушённо.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d54"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d54",
          "order": 54,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "pause_before": 1.0,
          "text": "Глаза постепенно привыкают к темноте.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d55"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d55",
          "order": 55,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "Ты начинаешь видеть движение между корней.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d56"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d56",
          "order": 56,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "И скользишь вперёд почти бесшумно.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d57"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d57",
          "order": 57,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "— О-о-о…",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d58"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d58",
          "order": 58,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_tunnel",
          "text": "— Вот это уже моя территория.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d70"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d60",
          "order": 60,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_rocky",
          "transition_before": "fade_in",
          "text": "Подъём оказывается тяжёлым.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d61"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d61",
          "order": 61,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_rocky",
          "text": "Острые камни режут лапы.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d62"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d62",
          "order": 62,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_rocky",
          "text": "Ветер становится всё сильнее.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d63"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d63",
          "order": 63,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_forest_rocky",
          "text": "Но постепенно ты поднимаешься выше леса.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d64"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d64",
          "order": 64,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_panoramic_view",
          "transition_before": "fade_in",
          "camera_effect": "slow_zoom_out",
          "text": "Перед тобой раскрывается весь лес.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d65"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d65",
          "order": 65,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_panoramic_view",
          "text": "Река блестит далеко внизу.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d66"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d66",
          "order": 66,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_panoramic_view",
          "text": "А среди тумана поднимаются башни.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d67"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d67",
          "order": 67,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_panoramic_view",
          "text": "— А вот это уже полезно.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d70"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d70",
          "order": 70,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "transition_before": "fade_out_in",
          "text": "Какой бы путь ты ни выбрал, лес всё равно приводит тебя сюда.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d71"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d71",
          "order": 71,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "text": "Дорога оказывается полностью перекрыта.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d72"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d72",
          "order": 72,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "text": "Перед тобой лежит гигантское вывернутое дерево.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d73"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d73",
          "order": 73,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "camera_effect": "slow_zoom_in",
          "text": "Корни торчат из земли как рёбра мёртвого чудовища.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d74"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d74",
          "order": 74,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "text": "Толстые ветви переплелись в сплошную стену.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d75"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d75",
          "order": 75,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "pause_before": 1.5,
          "text": "— Да вы издеваетесь…",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d76"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d76",
          "order": 76,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "text": "— Это уже не дерево.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d77"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d77",
          "order": 77,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_fallen_tree",
          "text": "— Это полноценная крепость.",
          "has_choices": true,
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d77_c1",
              "text": "Перепрыгнуть.",
              "effects": {
                "activity": 0.10,
                "impulsivity": 0.07,
                "selfControl": -0.07
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d90"
            },
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d77_c2",
              "text": "Найти обход.",
              "effects": {
                "anxiety": 0.07,
                "selfControl": 0.07,
                "activity": -0.05
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d100"
            },
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d77_c3",
              "text": "Построить себе проход.",
              "effects": {
                "adaptability": 0.10,
                "rigidity": -0.05
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d110"
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d90",
          "order": 90,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "Ты резко срываешься с места.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d91"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d91",
          "order": 91,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "Прыжок.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d92"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d92",
          "order": 92,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "Ещё один.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d93"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d93",
          "order": 93,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "Когти впиваются в мокрую кору.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d94"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d94",
          "order": 94,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "На мгновение кажется, что ты сорвёшься вниз.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d95"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d95",
          "order": 95,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "Но уже через секунду ты перелетаешь через преграду.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d96"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d96",
          "order": 96,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "— ХА!",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d97"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d97",
          "order": 97,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_top",
          "text": "— Всё ещё великолепен.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d120"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d100",
          "order": 100,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_ivy_thicket",
          "text": "Ты сворачиваешь к густым зарослям.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d101"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d101",
          "order": 101,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_ivy_thicket",
          "text": "Работа оказывается долгой и грязной.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d102"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d102",
          "order": 102,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_ivy_thicket",
          "text": "Колючки цепляются за одежду.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d103"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d103",
          "order": 103,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_ivy_thicket",
          "text": "Влажные ветви бьют по морде.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d104"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d104",
          "order": 104,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_ivy_thicket",
          "text": "Но постепенно ты находишь безопасный путь.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d105"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d105",
          "order": 105,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_ivy_thicket",
          "text": "— Иногда быть умнее ужасно скучно.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d120"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d110",
          "order": 110,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "text": "Ты внимательно изучаешь преграду.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d111"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d111",
          "order": 111,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "text": "Потом начинаешь собирать конструкцию.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d112"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d112",
          "order": 112,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "text": "Брёвна.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d113"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d113",
          "order": 113,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "text": "Сучья.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d114"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d114",
          "order": 114,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "text": "Плоские камни.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d115"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d115",
          "order": 115,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "pause_before": 1.0,
          "text": "Через некоторое время перед тобой уже стоит мост.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d116"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d116",
          "order": 116,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_tree_base",
          "text": "— Интеллект — страшное оружие.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d120"
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d120",
          "order": 120,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "transition_before": "darkening",
          "text": "Едва ты оказываешься по другую сторону дерева, под листвой что-то блестит.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d121"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d121",
          "order": 121,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "camera_effect": "slow_zoom_in",
          "text": "Ты разгребаешь листья лапой.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d122"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d122",
          "order": 122,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "Кости.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d123"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d123",
          "order": 123,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "Старая человеческая кисть.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d124"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d124",
          "order": 124,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "А на пальце — массивное кольцо.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d125"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d125",
          "order": 125,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "pause_before": 2.0,
          "text": "— Ох, прекрасно.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d126"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d126",
          "order": 126,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "— Древний лес.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d127"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d127",
          "order": 127,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "— Мертвецы.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d128"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d128",
          "order": 128,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "— Странное кольцо.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d129"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d129",
          "order": 129,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_bone_clearing",
          "text": "— Всё как я люблю.",
          "has_choices": true,
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d129_c1",
              "text": "Забрать кольцо.",
              "effects": {
                "egoFocus": 0.07,
                "negativeAffect": 0.05,
                "emotionalSensitivity": -0.07
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d140"
            },
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d129_c2",
              "text": "Похоронить кости.",
              "effects": {
                "emotionalSensitivity": 0.07,
                "rigidity": 0.05,
                "negativeAffect": -0.05
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d140"
            },
            {
              "id": "ch2_s1_d129_c3",
              "text": "Уйти отсюда.",
              "effects": {
                "anxiety": 0.07,
                "selfControl": 0.05,
                "activity": -0.05
              },
              "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d140"
            }
          ]
        },

        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d140",
          "order": 140,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "transition_before": "fade_out_in",
          "text": "Постепенно деревья начинают редеть.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d141"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d141",
          "order": 141,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "text": "Туман расступается.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d142"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d142",
          "order": 142,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "text": "И впереди появляются огромные каменные башни.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d143"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d143",
          "order": 143,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "camera_effect": "slow_zoom_out",
          "text": "Древний Лес остаётся позади.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d144"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d144",
          "order": 144,
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "text": "Но ощущение чужого взгляда всё ещё не отпускает тебя.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d145"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d145",
          "order": 145,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "pause_before": 2.0,
          "text": "— Ну что ж…",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": "ch2_s1_d146"
        },
        {
          "id": "ch2_s1_d146",
          "order": 146,
          "speaker": "Cat",
          "background": "bg_ch2_valley_towers",
          "text": "— А вот теперь начинаются настоящие проблемы.",
          "has_choices": false,
          "next_dialogue": null
        }

      ]
    }
  ]
}
